snippet.title: Best VGM 2197 - Ys VIII : Lacrimosa of Dana - Eroded Valley
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Switch / PS4 / Vita
Ys VIII : Lacrimosa of Dana (2016)
Eroded Valley
Hayato Sonoda & Takahiro Unisuga
